<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>Password Reset</title>
	<style>
		/* CSS styles for the email template */
		body {
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			background-color: #f4f4f4;
		}

		.container {
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding: 20px;
			background-color: #ffffff;
			border-radius: 4px;
			box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		}

		h2 {
			color: #333333;
			font-size: 24px;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		p {
			color: #555555;
			font-size: 16px;
			line-height: 1.5;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		.cta-button {
			display: inline-block;
			padding: 12px 24px;
			background-color: #4caf50;
			color: #ffffff;
			text-decoration: none;
			border-radius: 4px;
			font-weight: bold;
			margin-top: 20px;
		}

		.footer {
			color: #999999;
			font-size: 14px;
		}

		.image-container {
			text-align: center;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		img {
			max-width: 100%;
			height: auto;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="image-container">
			<img src="https://vc-development-public.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/stg-everyticket/assets/static/images/acc-verify.svg"
				alt="Email Image" />


		</div>
		<br>
		<h2>Password Reset</h2>
		<p>We received a request to reset your password. Please click the button below to proceed:</p>
		<a href="<%= locals.target_url%>" class="cta-button">Reset Password</a>
		<p>If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste the following URL into your browser:</p>
		<p><a href="<%= locals.target_url%>">
				<%= locals.target_url%>
			</a></p>
		<p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
		<p>
			If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact our support team at
			<a href="mailto:vc-angular@yopmail.com">vc-angular@yopmail.com</a>.
		</p>
		<p class="footer">Best regards,<br />VC Angular</p>
	</div>
</body>

</html>